    {
      "para_id": "Q009693.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Annunītum of Agade , his lady , Enlil-bani , the shepherd , who makes everything abundant for Nibru , the powerful king , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the spouse chosen in the heart by Inana , built the Ulmaš , her beloved temple in Isin ."
    }
  ],
